{"tid":405391,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"LOL香港軍團 召集 鍾意一齊打機既你","createTime":"2017-09-18T23:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T02:44:58.000Z","uid":133141,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38ad8b315cf2638174e4a65ad2d6ceca79e6beb1","tid":405391,"uid":133141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T23:02:28.000Z","msg":"19/9/2017<br />\n開個軍團想大家有時自己一個打機好悶 <br />\n可以有朋友仔一齊玩(我認我邊緣人)<br />\n多個圈子一齊玩下 新手老手都歡迎<br />\n之前其實都開過 都多巴打絲打 比例2:1到 但因為最後有人搞小圈子 所以不告又終我解散左。<br />\n依加想開返個新既軍團 希望巴絲打們 鍾意一齊打下機 得閒打下自訂咁<br />\n巴絲打可以留低你個ID或者加我 我ID係:動感鮑魚<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hdwallpapersfreedownload.com/uploads/large/games/league-of-legends-hd-photos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hdwallpapersfreedownload.com%2Fuploads%2Flarge%2Fgames%2Fleague-of-legends-hd-photos.jpg&h=149bbc94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ec4c275f62cd8148ef471b2ce1734f9338cf911","tid":405391,"uid":133141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T23:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079536be938fb1a42abee458d1b49fec8112bbc2","tid":405391,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T00:45:48.000Z","msg":"有得小圈子真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期銅牌垃圾仔表示無法取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b740be81a3dae7575f1dbb1bce53db56422fa961","tid":405391,"uid":133141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有得小圈子真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期銅牌垃圾仔表示無法取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊玩啦巴打"},{"pid":"a50c4da75f49bcb1307e87698754edb4d2d64fee","tid":405391,"uid":133141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.g